hadiths[37]{hadithnumber,text}:
1161,"Ibad bin Tameem apney chacha ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish ki dua ke liye logon ke sath mein bahir ( maidan mein) nikley. aapney unhen do rakatein padhain. in mein qirat oonchi aawaz se ki, aapney apni chadar ko ultaya, apney haath utha kar dua farmae aur barish maangi aur qibla rukh huey."
1162,"Janab Ibad bin Tameem Mazni ne bayan kiya ke unhoney apney chacha se suna, jo ke as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se they, wo bayan kar rahey they : eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze-istisqaa ke liye nikley . aapney logon ki taraf peeth karkey Shan wale Allah se dua maangi. Sulaiman bin Dawood ka bayan hai : aapney qibley ki taraf rukh kiya aur apni chadar ko ultaya phir do rakatein padhin. ibne-Abi Zi'ib ne kaha : aapney in mein qirat ki . ibne sarah ne ye izafa kiya hai : maqsad ye hai ke aapney jahri qirat ki ."
1163,"Janab Muhammad bin muslim) ibne-Shahab Zohri ( ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki, magar Namaz ka zikr nahin kiya aur kaha : aapney apni chadar ko paltaayaa . is tarah ke uska daayan kinara apney baeyn kandhey par aur baayan kinara daain kandhey par kar liya phir Shan wale Allah se dua farmaee."
1164,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz istisqaa padhaai , aap par siyah rang ki ooni chadar thi. aapney chaha ke uskey nichey waley kinarey ko pakad kar ooper kar lein , magar ye aap ke liye mushkil ho gaya to aapney usey kandhon hi par palat liya."
1165,"Janab Is'haq bin Abdullah kehtey hain ke mujhey Ameere-Madina Waleed bin Utba ne . ... Usman ne usko ibne Aqba kaha . ... . Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan bheja ke main un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz istisqaa ke mutalliq poochh kar aaun . to unhoney bayan kiya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maamuli haalat mein tawaazeh aur aajizi ki kaifiyat ke sath nikley. yahan tak ke Namaz gaah mein pahunch gaey . Usman ne izafa kiya ke aap member par chadhey. phir dono ka muttafiqa bayan hai : aapney tumharey un khutbon  ki manind khutba nahin diya, balke musalsal dua , izhare-ijz (khidmat) aur takbir mein mashghool rahey. phir do rakatein padhein jaisey ke eid mein padhi jati hain. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye riwayat Nufaili Nufaili ki hai. aur ibne-Utba ( تاء (ta) ke sath ( sahih hai."
1166,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz istisqaa ke liye Namaz gaah ki taraf nikley . aapney jab dua ka irada farmaya to qibley ki taraf rukh kar liya aur apni chadar palat li.
1167,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid Mazini (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz gaah ki taraf nikley aur Namaz istisqaa padhi aur jab qibley ki taraf rukh kiya to apni chadar palti.
1168,"Hazrat Umair Maula bani aabi Laham (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maqame-zauraa ke qarib ahjaar zait ke paas barish ki dua kartey dekha, aap apney chehrey ke samney haath uthaey khadey they, magar haath sar se unchey na they."
1169,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch log ( barish na barasney ki wajeh sey) rotey huey aaye to aapney yun dua farmaee : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! اسْقِنَا غَيْثًا مُغِيثًا مَرِيئًا مَرِيعًا نَافِعًا غَيْرَ ضَارٍّ عَاجِلًا غَيْرَ آجِلٍ ) ''aey Allah ! hamen barish inayat farma , had se zyada faydemand, madadgar , behtareen anjam wali, jo shadabi laye, nafa aawar ho, kisi zarar (nuksan) ka baais na baney aur jaldi aaye , der na karey. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke . . . . . (us dua ke baad fauran) un par badal chha gaya."
1170,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi dua mein apney haath itney buland na kartey they jitney ke istisqaa mein , yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi dikhai deti thi."
1171,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish ke liye is tarah dua kartey they, aur unhoney haath lambey karkey dikhaye aur hatheliyon ko zameen ki taraf kiya, (aur itney buland kiye ke) maine unki baghlon ki safedi dekhi."
1172,Janab Muhammad bin Ibrahim kehtey hain ke mujhey un sahab ne khabar di jinhonne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ahjaar zait ke paas apni hatheliyan phailaey dua kartey dekha tha. ( guzishta hadees : 1168 (
1173,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki ke barish nahin ho rahi to aapney Namaz gaah mein member rakhney ka hukm diya aur logon se eik din ka wada kiya ke wo us mein bahir ayen. Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us roz ( Namaz istisqaa ke liye (us waqt nikley jab Suraj ki tikiya nikal aai thi , aap member par baithey aur Shan wale Allah ki takbir aur tahmeed ki, phir farmaya : ''tum ne shikayat ki hai ke tumharey ilaqey khushk ho rahey hain aur barish main apni aamad ke waqt se takheer ho rahi hai. to Shan wale Allah ne tumhen hukm diya hai ke usey pukaro , aur tum se uska wada hai ke wo qubul kerega.'' phir farmaya : '' tamam tareefen Allah ke liye hain jo tamam jahano ka paalney wala hai. be-inteha rehem kerney wala aur meharban hai. badle ke din ka badshah hai. Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. wo jo chahta hai karta hai. aey Allah ! to hi Allah hai, terey siwa aur koi mabud nahin, to ghani aur be-parwa hai aur ham faqeer aur mohtaj hain, ham par barish nazil farma aur jo to nazil farmaai usey hamarey liye quwat aur eik waqt tak ke liye guzraan bana dey.'' phir aapney apney haath uthaey aur uthatey gaey, yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi dikhai deney lagi . phir aapney logon ki taraf peeth kar li (yani qibla rukh ho gaey (aur apni chadar paltaai jabke aap apney haath uthaey huey they. baad Azan logon ki taraf munh kiya aur member se utar aaye aur do rakatein padhain. tab Allah ne eik badli paida farmaee, wo kadaki aur chamki aur Allah ke hukm se barasney lagi , aap apni masjid tak na pahunchey ke naaley bahney lagey. jab aapney logon ko dekha ke wo sayon aur chhapparon ki taraf jaldi jaldi bhag rahey hain to aap hansey , yahan tak ke aap ki daadhen nazar aaney lagin. aapney farmaya : ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah taala her chiz par qadir hai aur main Allah ka banda aur uska Rasool hun.''  Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ye hadees ghareeb hai. (yani iskey riwayton mein tafarrud hai) aur sanad ke aetbar se jaiyed ( umda ( hai. (yani is mein koi illat qadiha nahin.) aur ye hadees ehale-Madina ki daleel hai ke wo log ( ملك يوم الدين ( padhtey hain."
1174,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ehale-Madina ko qehat (sukha) pesh aaya. Jumey ka din tha aap hamein khutba irshad farma rahey they ke eik aadmi khada ho gaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ghodey mar gaey, bakriyan halak ho gaeen , Allah se dua farmaeyn ke hamein barish inayat farmaai . aapney apney haath phailaey aur dua ki . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aasman shishey ki manind saaf tha, so hawa chalney lagi aur badal ka eik tukda namoodaar hua aur phailtaa chala gaya , phir aasman ne apna dahaana khol diya. ham jo ( Namaz padh kar) nikley to pani mein se guzartey huey apney gharon ko pahunchey. phir barish hoti rahi aur agley Jumey tak hoti rahi. tab wohi aadmi ya koi doosra khada hua aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ghar girney lagey hain, Allah se dua farmaeyn ke is barish ko rok dey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskuraaey aur dua farmaee : ''(aey Allah ! ye barish) hamarey ird-gird ho, hamarey ooper na ho.'' ( Anas ne kaha ( maine badal ko dekha ke wo Madiney ke ird-gird phatney laga goya ke wo (Madina) aisey ho gaya jaisey taaj."
1175,Shareek bin Abdullah bin Ubai Namir ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna aur hadees Abdul-Azeez (yani sabiqa hadees ( ki manind zikr kiya aur (us mein izafa bayan kartey huey ( kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney dono haath apney chehrey ke barabar uthaey aur dua farmaney lagey : (اللهم اسقنا . . الخ) aur usi ki jaisi hadees bayan ki.
1176,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab barish ke liye dua farmatey to yun kehtey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! اسْقِ عِبَادَكَ وَبَهَائِمَكَ وَانْشُرْ رَحْمَتَكَ وَأَحْيِ بَلَدَكَ الْمَيِّتَ ) ''aey Allah ! apney bandon aur apney janweron ko pani pila . apni rehmat aam kar dey aur apni khushk zameen ko tar-o-taza kar dey.'' ye Malik ki hadees ke lafz hain."
1177,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khoob qiyam kiya. aap logon ke sath qiyam farmatey, phir rukoo kartey , phir khadey hotey . phir rukoo kartey , phir khadey hotey , phir rukoo kartey. chunanche aapney do rakatein padhaeen. her rakaat mein teen rukoo kiye , teesra rukoo farmatey, phir sajda kartey. yahan tak ke kuch logon ko us din tool (lambe) qiyam ki wajeh se ghashi honey lagi yahan tak ke pani ke dol un par daley gaey. aap jab rukoo ko jatey to ( الله اكبر ( kehtey aur jab sar uthatey to (سمع الله لمن حمده) kehtey . yahan tak ke Suraj saaf ho gaya. phir aapney farmaya : '' Suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut ya zindagi ki wajeh se be-Noor nahin hotey balke ye Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. wo inke zariey se apney bandon ko darata hai, so jab ye be Noor ho jaeyn to Namaz ki taraf jaldi kiya karo.''"
1178,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan hua aur ye wohi din tha jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farzand Janab Ibrahim faut huey they to logon ne kaha : ye Ibrahim ki wafat par gahan aayaa hai. so Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qiyam farmaya aur logon ko chaar sajdon mein chhe rukoo karaaey. (yani her rakaat mein teen-teen rukoo kiye.) aapney ( الله اكبر ( kaha : phir lambi qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya. is qadr jitna ke qiyam kiya tha. phir sar uthaya aur qirat ki jo ke pehli qirat se kam thi. phir rukoo kiya jitna ke qiyam kiya tha. phir sar uthaya aur teesri baar qirat ki jo ke dusri baar ki qirat se kam thi. phir rukoo kiya jis qadr ke qiyam kiya tha. phir sar uthaya aur sajdey mein chaley gaey aur do sajdey kiye. phir khadey huey aur teen rukoo kiye , sajdey se pahley. har pehla rukoo doosrey se ziyada lamba hota tha, albatta har rukoo qiyam ke barabar lamba hota tha. (Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( bayan kiya ke phir aap Namaz ke beech mein peechhey hatey to safein bhi aap ke sath peechhey ho gaeen , phir aap aagey badhey aur apni jagah par khadey ho gaey to safein bhi aagey badh gaeen , is tarah aapney Namaz puri ki yahan tak ke Suraj saaf nikal aaya . phir aapney farmaya : logo ! Suraj aur chaand Shan wale Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. ye kisi insan ki maut ke baais be Noor nahin hotey . jab tum in mein se kuch dekho to Namaz padha karo yahan tak ke saaf ho jaeyn.'' aur baqiya hadees bayan ki."
1179,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik intehai garm din mein Suraj gahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney as-haab ko Namaz padhaai aur lamba qiyam kiya yahan tak ke log girney lagey. phir aapney rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya. phir aapney sar uthaya aur lambi der tak khadey rahey. phir (doosra) rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya phir sar uthaya aur lambi der khadey rahey phir sajda kiya aur do sajdey kiye phir qiyam kiya jaisey ke pahley kiya tha. so aapney chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye aur hadees bayan ki.
1180,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mutahra (paak biwi) Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein Suraj gahan hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye aur khadey huey aur takbir kahi aur logon ne aap ke peechhey safein banaeen, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qirat shuru ki aur lambi qirat ki . phir aapney takbir kahi aur rukoo kiya, lamba rukoo , phir apna sar uthaya aur kaha : (سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد) aur khadey rahey aur qirat ki, lambi qirat , jo ke pehli qirat se kam thi , phir aapney takbir kahi aur rukoo kiya, lamba rukoo , magar pehley rukoo se kam. phir kaha : (سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد) phir dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kiya aur chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey mukammal kiye aur aap ke farigh honey se pehley Suraj saaf ho gaya."
1181,Saiyedna Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Suraj gahan mein Namaz padhi jaisey ke Urwa an Aaysha an Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki (mazkura baala) hadees mein guzra hai. yani aapney do rakatein padhaeen aur her rakaat mein do rukoo kiye.
1182,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan hua aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Namaz padhaai aur lambi soorton mein se eik surat ki qirat ki aur paanch rukoo aur do sajdey kiye phir dusri rakaat mein khadey huey aur lambi soorton mein se eik surat padhi aur paanch rukoo aur do sajdey kiye phir aap qibla rukh ho kar baithey aur dua kartey rahey, yahan tak ke Suraj saaf ho gaya."
1183,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney Suraj gahan mein Namaz padhaai to qirat ki aur rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki aur rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki aur rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki aur rukoo kiya, phir sajda kiya aur dusri rakaat mein bhi aisey hi kiya."
1184,"Janab Saulba bin Ibaad Abdi . ... . ehale-Basra mein se eik shakhs . ... bayan kartey hain ke wo Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik khutbey mein hazir huye, Samura ne kaha : eik dafa mein aur eik Ansari naujawan nishana bazi kar rahey they yahan tak ke dekhney waley ki aankh mein jab Suraj ufuq se do ya teen neze par tha to wo siyah ho gaya jaisey ke tanuma (ghaas) ho. ham mein se eik ne apney sathi se kaha : chalo aao masjid ki taraf chalen, qasam Allah ki ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Suraj ki is kaifiyat mein ummat ko zarur koi naee baat taaleem farmaeyn gey . so ham fauran wahan pahunch gaey ( jaisey goya hamein dhakel diya gaya ho) to wahan aap ghar se tashrif laye huey they. isliye aap aagey badhey aur Namaz padhaai. aapney hamein nihayat taweel qiyam karaya aisa ke kisi bhi Namaz mein aapney hamein nahin karaya tha. ham aap ki aawaz nahin sun rahey they. phir aapney hamein nihayat taweel rukoo karaya jo kisi bhi Namaz mein aapney hamein nahin karaya tha. ham aap ki aawaz nahin sun rahey they. phir aapney hamein nihayat taweel sajda karaya jo kisi bhi Namaz mein aapney hamein nahin karaya tha. ham aap ki aawaz nahin sun rahey they. phir dusri rakaat mein bhi aapney aisey hi kiya. aur dusri rakaat mein baithney ke dauran mein Suraj saaf ho gaya. phir aapney salam phera . phir khadey huye, Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki, Allah ki tauheed aur apni Abdiyat aur risaalat ki shahadat di. aur Ahmed bin Yunus ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khutba bayan kiya."
1185,"Hazrat Qabisa Hilaali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan aa gaya. isliye aap ghabraey huey, apna kapda ghaseet'tey huey nikley . main un dino aap ke sath Madiney mein tha. aapney do rakatein padhaeen aur un mein kafi lamba qiyam kiya, farigh huey to Suraj saaf ho chuka tha. aapney farmaya : ''ye nishaniyan hain. Shan wala Allah unke zariey se ( bandon ko) darata hai. so jab tum ye dekho to Namaz padho jaisey ke tum ne abhi qaribi farz Namaz padhi hai.''"
1186,Hazrat Qabisa Hilaali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Suraj ko gahan laga . aur Musa bin-Ismail ki) mazkura baala ( hadees ki manind bayan kiya. is mein bayan kiya : yahan tak ke sitarey zahir ho gaey.
1187,"Ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan aayaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley aur logon ko Namaz padhaaney ke liye khadey huey . isliye maine aap ki qirat ka andaza lagaya to mehsoos kiya ke aapney Sura Baqara tilawat farmaai hai. aur hadees bayan ki . phir aapney do sajdey kiye , phir khadey huey aur lambi qirat ki . maine aap ki qirat ka andaza lagaya to maine samjha ke aapney Sura Aale-Imran tilawat ki hai."
1188,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lambi qirat ki aur oonchi aawaz se. yani Namaze-Kusoof mein .
1189,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : Suraj gahan hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi , log aap ke sath they. aapney sura baqara ke qarib lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya. aur baqi hadees bayan ki."
1190,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Suraj gahan aayaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko hukm diya usney aelan kya : ( الصلاة جامعة ( yani Namaz ke liye jama ho jao.
1191,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut ya wiladat ki wajeh se nahin gahnaatey . jab tum ye ( kaifiyat ( dekho to Shan wale Allah se dua kiya karo, uski takbir bayan karo aur sadqa diya karo.''"
1192,Sayeda Asma binte-Abi Bakr Siddiq (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz-Kusoof ke mauqe par ghulam azad kerney ka hukm diya kartey they.
1193,Hazrat Nauman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Suraj ko gahan laga to aap do do rakatein padhney lagey aur Suraj ke mutalliq bhi daryaft farmatey jatey they yahan tak ke wo saaf ho gaya.
1194,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Suraj gahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qiyam kiya, ( itna lamba qiyam kiya ke) lagta tha ke aap rukoo nahin karengey . phir rukoo kiya, ( itna lamba rukoo kiya ke) lagta tha ke aap rukoo se sar nahin uthaeyn gey phir sar uthaya , ( itna lamba qiyam kiya ke) lagta tha ke aap sajda nahin karengey phir sajda kiya, (itna lamba sajda kiya ke) lagta tha ke aap sajdey se sar nahin uthaeyn gey phir sar uthaya aur (itni der baithey rahey ke) lagta tha ke aap sajda nahin karengey phir sajda kiya ( itna lamba sajda kiya ke) lagta tha ke aap sar nahin uthaeyn gey phir sar uthaya aur dusri rakaat mein bhi aisey hi kiya. aur aakhiri sajdey mein zor-zor se saans leney lagey aur ''uff-uff'' ki aawaz nikali aur kaha : ''aey merey rab ! kya to ne mujh se wada nahin kiya hai ke jab tak mein in mein mojud hun inko azab nahin dega . kiya to ne mujh se wada nahin kiya hai ke jab tak ye istighfar kartey rahengey to inko azab na dega.'' gharz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to Suraj saaf ho chuka tha. ... . aur hadees bayan ki."
1195,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke daure-Risaalat ki baat hai. main teer andazi ki mashq kar raha tha ke Suraj gahan lag gaya to maine teer phenk diye aur kaha : main bil-zaroor dekhun ga ke aaj Suraj gahan waley din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya naya kaam kartey hain, chunanche main aap ke paas pahuncha aur dekha ke aap apney haath uthaey tasbih , tahmeed aur tahleel mein mashghool dua kar rahey they yahan tak ke Suraj saaf ho gaya. is mauqe par aapney do rakaaton mein do suraten padhein ."
1196,Janab Ubaidullah bin Nazar se riwayat hai ke unke walid ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki zindagi main eik roz ( aandhi ya badal ki wajeh sey) andhera chha gaya to main Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Abu-Hamza ! kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein bhi aap logon ko aisi kaifiyat se do chaar hona padta tha? unhoney kaha : Allah ki panah ! agar hawa bhi tez ho jati to ham jaldi jaldi masjid ka rukh kartey they ke kahin qiyamat na aa jaey.
1197,Janab Ikrima kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko khabar di gaee ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaj mein se falan faut ho gaee hain to aap sajdey mein gir gaey. un se kaha gaya ke aap is mauqe par sajda kartey hain? to unhoney jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jab koi bada waqia ya hadisa dekho to sajda kiya karo.'' aur bhala zaujae-nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat se badh kar bhi koi hadisa hoga?
